      *****************************************************************
       01  ETCL9127-ROTINA              PIC  X(10)  VALUE 'ETR90127'.
       01  ETCL9127-DATA.
           05 ETCL9127-VERSAO           PIC  X(03) VALUE SPACES.
              88 ETCL9127-V203                     VALUE '203'.
              88 ETCL9127-V300                     VALUE '300'.
              88 ETCL9127-VVAL                     VALUE '203' '300'.
